  "title": "GPT-5 王者归来？奥特曼称 AI 已跨科学门槛，三大学科正迎来实质性突破",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652633206&idx=2&sn=5216b115a3b46a4d385024f04086c890",
